Package view.SetupGame

Class LoadGamePanel

java.lang.Object
java.awt.Component
java.awt.Container
javax.swing.JComponent
javax.swing.JPanel
view.SetupGame.LoadGamePanel
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible, StartGame
public class LoadGamePanel
extends javax.swing.JPanel
implements StartGame
The class Load game panel shows a list of previous games started by the user, so that they can keep the game configuration and start a new game with it. It is a BorderLayout with several components including JComboBox, JPanel, JButton, JTextField. The view will use the controller to register all user inputs.
